tc qdisc del dev ifb0 root
tc qdisc del dev eth0 root

sleep 3

tc qdisc add dev eth0 root netem loss 100%
tc qdisc add dev ifb0 root netem loss 100%

sleep 3

tc qdisc del dev ifb0 root
tc qdisc del dev eth0 root

sleep 3

tc qdisc add dev eth0 root netem loss 100%
tc qdisc add dev ifb0 root netem loss 100%
